  <title>Move and Groove</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col bg-muted">
          <hr>
           <p class="text-muted font-weight-bold">Your path to a healthy lifestyle</p>
          
        <p>Move and Groove is your ultimate service for tracking physical exercise. It started out as a private fitness tracker but seeing the need, it is now gone public and incorporates several dozen other exercise types, including indoor and outdoor activities. </p>
        <p>Ready to change your life and get fit? <%= link_to "Sign up now", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %> If you are already a member <%= link_to "Login now", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %></p>
      </div>  
      </div>
  <hr>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="card border-white text-info" style="height: 30rem;">
          <%= image_tag "jogging.jpeg" %>
      <div class="card-body bg-light">
        <h5 class="card-title">Our Company</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Move & Groove</h6>
    <p class="card-text">We inspires, educates, and connects athletes and community to have the best lifestyle.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="card  border-white text-info" style="height: 14rem;">
        <%= image_tag "clara.png" %>
        <div class="card-body bg-light">
        <h5 class="card-title">Our Founder</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Clara Dunn</h6>
    <p class="card-text">Started the company in 2014 at her home in Boston and grew tremendous success. </p>
    </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">  
    <div class="card broder-white text-info" style="height: 14rem;">
      <img src="https://st.depositphotos.com/2650957/5104/i/450/depositphotos_51049563-stock-photo-mission-button-on-virtual-screen.jpg" alt="">
        <div class="card-body bg-light">
        <h5 class="card-title">Our Culture</h5>
         <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Mission & Vision</h6>
    <p class="card-text">Inspires, educates, and connects athletes, and community to maintain a healthy lifestyle.</p>
    </div>
      </div>
    </div>
     </div>
      <br>
      <hr>
    </div>


   </div>
      </div>
